link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=87f744e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"f0ba71ba8600795de6c83dc5a3f3959c38c26257","tid":1547180,"uid":271495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"共享大灣區啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba4af94179d9d7409f553725b8076ab103dad45","tid":1547180,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"有祖國不愛，要去等二到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60303025ef1b341d976ddbe66acc0844f8d3877f","tid":1547180,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"放習近平個朵,傻b死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5911bf7fe87192d3358777d1c90ee25f0d5d0730","tid":1547180,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor