aces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44352c80862d1b0e6e18826bc59c96b53fcd88f0","tid":1547180,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] <br />\n907 機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=667bac23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n908 美領<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hk908ch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk908ch&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2gZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=24d469f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk908ch</a><br />\n<br />\n907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a> <br />\n<br />\n我係機場保安7號嗰日有少少野想同大家講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543735</a><br />\n<br />\n612 黑警暴力，<br />\n721 元朗恐襲，<br />\n811 黑警恐襲，<br />\n831 太子恐襲，<br />\n中共、港共、警畜、鄉黑、黨鐵聯手令香港進入軍管時代，法治人權蕩然無存。<br />\n犧牲左9位殉港義士， 被捕人數過千，當中近百人被控暴動，面臨十年牢獄生涯， <br />\n無數傷者爆眼、甩牙、骨折、腦出血、傷殘、性凌辱，仲有白色恐怖令到數唔清嘅受傷手足唔敢求醫。<br />\n<br />\n再講多次 犧牲左咁多換黎一個姍姍來遲嘅所謂「撤回」，你仲覺得可以收貨咩？<br />\n記住，五大訴求，缺一不可，輸咗呢次，係一定會輸突成個香港！<br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄唔好停！黎緊街頭見！機場見！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"d15d195a81791fe0b9fe3541e7722098d560c8d6","tid":1547180,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"愈高層愈鍾意去外國住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4b706c7172e5d37a828697a755cb1e3e0d7eab","tid":1547180,"uid":58826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"一世做中國人"},{"pid":"2a3aadc436ff1ef8c74050a2fbb868a2fe99a2c2","tid":1547180,"uid":246741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"愛国就要一生留在国家啊!"},{"pid":"2bc750af3307f69e72d27f1fd318d64